                        <p>只要在此留下器捐意願，家屬隨時可上網查詢確認你的意願</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 organ-donation-form form-page tag-box-v2">

                <form action="" method="POST" class="" role="form">
                    <div class="col-xs-6">
                        <label class="radio content-boxes-v1 radio-v1"><input type="radio" name="radio" checked><i class="rounded-x"></i>全部器捐</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6">
